trailingComments.value:
*
 * Determines if the value is an object
 * @function IsObject
 * @param {any} value 
 * @return {boolean} Whether or not the value is an object
 * @example
 * IsObject() // false
 * IsObject(()=>{}) // false
 * IsObject('') // false
 * IsObject(true) // false
 * IsObject(null) // false
 * IsObject(new Date()) // false
 * IsObject([]) // false
 * IsObject({}) // true
